  <entry>
    <title>如何删除GitHub仓库的所用commit</title>
    <link href="https://siemenstutorials.github.io/posts/4a1536ed.html"/>
    <id>https://siemenstutorials.github.io/posts/4a1536ed.html</id>
    <published>2020-05-08T12:58:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-05-08T13:16:46.659Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="如何删除GitHub仓库的所用commit"><a href="#如何删除GitHub仓库的所用commit" class="headerlink" title="如何删除GitHub仓库的所用commit"></a><center>如何删除GitHub仓库的所用commit</center></h1><p>因个人的需要有时候的误提交可能会有多余的commit,这时候如何删除commit就是一个很D疼的事；今天看到一个大神写了这个教程，特copy至此作为个人工作需的一些记录以作备查，在此感谢大神<a href="https://p3terx.com/archives/github-warehouse-cleaning-delete-all-commit-records.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">P3TERX</a></p><p>1：新建一个空白分支</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git checkout --orphan latest_branch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2:添加所有文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add -A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3:提交</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git commit -am <span class="string">"."</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4：强制删除旧的分支，如果是 master</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch -D master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5：将当前分支重命名为 master</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch -m master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6：强制推送到远程仓库</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push -f origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>7:至此您将获得全新干净的仓库<br>本文内容源自<a href="https://p3terx.com/archives/github-warehouse-cleaning-delete-all-commit-records.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">P3TERX</a></p>]]></content>
    
